{"tid":1720781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戰略建議 - 各大學戰略定位","createTime":"2019-11-14T13:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T13:55:01.000Z","uid":108757,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"49681a214f81fdcb7f1f5305c878095822487876","tid":1720781,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:00:59.000Z","msg":"守大學等於和理塞，唔需要撤，但要做好長期準備。<br />\n中大︰東鐵+吐露港公路<br />\n理大︰紅隧<br />\n城大、浸大︰窩打老道+歌和老街+達之路<br />\n港大︰薄扶林道+般咸道<br />\n<br />\n建議大約係咁<br />\n<br />\n敵方策略︰<span style=\"color: red;\">圍而不攻</span>，牽制兵馬<br />\n我方對應策略︰<br />\n1. 只留哨兵，<span style=\"color: red;\">輪流值班</span>，輪番入HALL休息，養足精神<br />\n2. 維持穩定、<span style=\"color: red;\">安全補給線</span>，市民可以運物資支援<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">清洗TG殘留物</span>，特別係中大，要用<span style=\"color: red;\">番梘洗地</span>，盡量<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好瞓地</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">返HALL瞓</span>，如果唔係慢性毒死<br />\n<br />\n得閒咪研究下武器，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保持心境開朗，唔好太繃緊</span></span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c6188c119e95460e94800b2a67581cc1f6a76a","tid":1720781,"uid":174207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"你肯定人地攻唔入？<br />\n<br />\n凡事做最壞打算  屋企失火識唔識走 點樣走"},{"pid":"eb156e974193fd091f2d737e87a7e766e1ffbe72","tid":1720781,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:02:59.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6c68defe59809c04a3b51c759930ea6ea10b1649","tid":1720781,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65c6188c119e95460e94800b2a67581cc1f6a76a","tid":1720781,"uid":174207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"你肯定人地攻唔入？<br />\n<br />\n凡事做最壞打算  屋企失火識唔識走 點樣走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:05:10.000Z","msg":"攻得入咪走，走唔洗教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8aa3ddc614d075b95ba8f954c49255127832438","tid":1720781,"uid":131326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:06:40.000Z","msg":"黑警毅進狗死全家，落地獄，每日被過百萬市民詛咒你地絕對無好下場，信不信由你，我地唔會殺狗，唔會接狗仔狗女放學，狗閪警，你地可以24小時睇實家人與及狗仔女嗎？<br />\n<br />\n黑警毅進狗我屌你老母，吹撚脹?"},{"pid":"cf8b6bb5604ddbc6e553ad4919dc8b59d7edf7db","tid":1720781,"uid":21236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:07:00.000Z","msg":"敵人可以直升機空降"},{"pid":"f90b13df8b68cda1386c2f99d4cdb2b4672d4e09","tid":1720781,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"好似三國打仗咁, 如果得中大一個城池就死梗. 比人一圍唔使打就玩完. 我同意如果則邊有其他城池支援就唔同講法!<br />\n<br />\n中大塞吐露淘公路, 理公塞過海隧道, 城大浸會塞九龍塘<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">南北交通斷左, 尖咀去中環CBD都斷埋, 全港最繁忙既轉車站九龍塘都冇埋!</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁樣政府唔頂得幾耐, 商家佬而家一定叫緊救命! </span>你以為佢真係唔急? 禽晚班官會約埋食宵夜? 我肯定而家林鄭急到瀨屎!"},{"pid":"aa316578123e39ca5c5d5a76ae53d6d598cd8b4c","tid":1720781,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"保持心境開朗，唔好太繃緊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c6b6a933fd14c0746b95d88c27207062a44414","tid":1720781,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df854448098dbfe0593b493a00e56ec1ced96870","tid":1720781,"uid":236140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:13:14.000Z","msg":"吐露港你可以守幾多日，大把居民開始發癲 <br />\n<br />\n大埔道個班居民，連白車都call唔到"},{"pid":"c429e288cba6eb157faf2ea59fe95b014bc48880","tid":1720781,"uid":186074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df854448098dbfe0593b493a00e56ec1ced96870","tid":1720781,"uid":236140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:13:14.000Z","msg":"吐露港你可以守幾多日，大把居民開